---
title: Chinese Hoisin & Orange-Glazed Chicken with Jasmine Rice & Asian Greens
description: Yes, this delicious dish gets its addictive flavour from a fruity secret ingredient! Fresh orange juice provides a tangy, sweet touch to the fragrant sauce in this easy chicken stir-fry.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/5beba766ae08b53c6f664112-aedcf8ce.jpg
